<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要吹熄蠟燭的火時，<delay20 />
記得站在蛋糕前<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" /><delay8 />一口氣吹熄啊！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啦！<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使勁吹熄蠟燭吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了好了，<delay8 />吹熄蠟燭這個任務<delay20 />
就交給今天的主角<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />吧。<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />一口氣吹熄吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種時候<delay20 />就是要放膽去做！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，一口氣吹熄所有蠟燭吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你又多了一歲啊。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />你又變得更成熟了，<delay20 />
我很高興能夠像這樣幫你慶生，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生日快樂！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過話說回來，<delay8 />
你的慶生會還真熱鬧啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也有<delay8 />幫忙裝飾房間喔。<delay20 />
畢竟<delay8 />這是我重要的死黨的慶生會啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興能幫上忙！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些生日紙杯蛋糕
全部<delay8 />都是你的喔！<pageBreak />大可不用急著吃掉<delay8 />沒關係，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不會有人跟你搶的，<delay8 />放心吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了不讓你這個主角發現，<delay8 />
我們準備得可辛苦啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />驚喜就是要先瞞著對方，<delay20 />
這樣對方才會覺得驚訝，
也比較有趣吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天有你的慶生會<delay8 />
和我的慶生會，<delay8 />感覺很忙碌啊！<pageBreak />能夠度過這麼熱鬧的生日，<delay20 />
我實在是很高興啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我很健忘，<delay20 />
但我絕對不會<delay8 />忘記你的生日喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />誰叫你跟我同一天生啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的生日是元旦啊，<delay20 />
這日子挺吉利的嘛，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能在一年之初生下你，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想你的雙親<delay8 />一定也很高興吧！</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到你是在2月29日出生的，
真少見啊。<pageBreak />不過，<delay8 />就算四年才過一次生日，<delay20 />
但年紀還是會一年一年增加啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />出生在2月29日……<delay20 />
這可是超罕見的啊。
我很榮幸<delay8 />能參加這麼罕見的慶生會喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">生日是<tag a="90" b="35" arg="0xcd00" />月<tag a="90" b="36" arg="0xcd00" />日很好記，
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我好羨慕啊～<pageBreak />而且啊，<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是日期跟月分是一樣的數字，<delay8 />
感覺就挺吉利的咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在12月24日出生，<delay8 />
那應該常常一起慶祝<delay8 />
生日和聖誕節吧！？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是說，<delay8 />
你會既收到生日禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又收到聖誕禮物？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你生日那天是聖誕節啊。<delay20 />
有種「好事成雙」的感覺，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別喜氣咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這個皮納塔啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是專門為你製作的喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就<delay8 />盡情地敲吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />聽好囉……<delay frames="40" />
你要集中所有精神，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲開這個皮納塔喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會好好看著你<delay8 />
敲開這傢伙的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>